experience.description:
- Execution of security administrator functions (ASTRA LINUX SPECIAL EDITION, Secret Net Studio, Window 10, Kaspersky Internet Security, Dr. web), administrator of information protection means (Trusted Boot Hardware and Software Module "Sobol", Generator of noise on power supply circuits, grounding from side electromagnetic radiation and leads LGSH-503, Sonata-P3. 1, Protection equipment against acoustic reconnaissance "Sonata AV" model 1M and 3M, Access control system); 
