- Elaboration of organizational and planning documents and implementation of practical measures to protect information at the security objects;
- Delimitation of personal responsibility of officials for the operation of specific hardware, software and information resources, determining the procedure for forming and using information resources;
- Participation in investigations of computer incidents at defense facilities.

